snippet.title: Alien Attack - Gameplay - SEGA Genesis [Action 52]
snippet.description:
Alien Attack is one of the game listed in Action 52. Action 52 was released in 1993 for SEGA Genesis.

Developer - Active Enterprises Ltd./FarSight Technologies
Publisher - Active Enterprises Ltd.
Release - 1993
Platform - Genesis
ESRB Rating - E for all Platform

Action/Cheat Codes for Alien Attack

INFINITE LIVES - ATKB-CA3Y
INVINCIBILITY - RYMV-C6YG
ONE SHOT KILL ENEMIES - A2NB-CA4L

***Codes are from - http://tv-games.ru/forum/
***Some code may not work.
***INVINCIBILITY code hangs the game.
***The problem with the code in my device does not means it will causes in your one too.
